525	682	directus_files	0efda097-6ca5-4709-bc3a-f2b29a4dcece	{"folder":"7b914226-4789-48cf-a2f5-8f85b73f2f64","title":"Eleven Labs 2026 06 09 T14 13 19  S50 V3","filename_download":"ElevenLabs_2026-06-09T14_13_19__s50_v3.mp3","type":"audio/mpeg","storage":"local"}	{"folder":"7b914226-4789-48cf-a2f5-8f85b73f2f64","title":"Eleven Labs 2026 06 09 T14 13 19  S50 V3","filename_download":"ElevenLabs_2026-06-09T14_13_19__s50_v3.mp3","type":"audio/mpeg","storage":"local"}	\N	\N
527	684	listening_tests	d3307137-ae3c-4387-a33a-30b8d6a440d9	{"id":"d3307137-ae3c-4387-a33a-30b8d6a440d9","title":"Lakeside Park Facilities","slug":"lakeside-park-facilities","description":"An outdoor map of Lakeside Park featuring a central lake, entrances, paths, and various facilities.","level":"B2","accent":"British English","duration_seconds":null,"question_count":6,"is_free":true,"instruction_text":"Label the map below. Write the correct letter, A-H, next to Questions 1-6.","transcript":"Welcome everyone to Lakeside Park. I'm the head ranger, and I'd like to give you a quick overview of the park's layout so you can make the most of your visit today. You are all currently standing at the Main Entrance, looking into the park. Straight ahead of you, before you reach the lake, is a large building. This is the Visitor Centre. You can get detailed maps and information here. Now, many of you have asked about getting some food and drink. We used to have a small cafe just to the right of the Main Entrance, but that building is no longer open to the public; it's just for staff parking now. Instead, to find the new Cafe, you need to walk along the path that goes around the eastern side of the central lake. Keep walking right to the far side of the lake, and you'll find it near the North Gate. There's a building just beyond the cafe in the top corner, but don't go there as that's just a maintenance shed. If you are interested in renting out a rowing boat, the Boat Hire is also on the eastern side of the lake. Walk up the main east path, and it's right next to the water. Directly opposite the Boat Hire, on the other side of the east path, you'll see a beautiful area enclosed by hedges. This is the Rose Garden, which is currently in full bloom. Over on the western side of the park, there's plenty to do as well. As you walk up the west path from the Main Entrance, before you reach the Old Bridge, you'll see a large fenced-off area. This is the Children's Playground, which we recently expanded. Continuing further on the west path, you'll walk over the Old Bridge. Just past the bridge, on the left-hand side, is a lovely shaded spot. This is the Picnic Area, perfect for relaxing after a walk. We hope you have a wonderful day exploring Lakeside Park!","prosody_script":null,"date_created":"2026-06-10T14:42:52.557Z","date_updated":"2026-06-10T14:42:52.557Z","status":"published","metadata":{"schema_version":"visual_labelling_listening_v1","topic":"Lakeside Park","speaker_role":"Park Guide","visual_blueprint":{"visual_type":"map_labelling","description":"An outdoor map of Lakeside Park featuring a central lake, entrances, paths, and various facilities.","canvas_layout":"The Main Entrance is at the bottom centre. A path leads straight ahead towards the central lake. Paths diverge to go around the east and west sides of the lake. There is an Old Bridge on the west path. The North Gate is at the top centre.","fixed_orientation_landmarks":[{"name":"Main Entrance","position":"Bottom centre","visible_text_on_image":"Main Entrance","why_safe_to_show":"Starting point for orientation."},{"name":"Central Lake","position":"Middle of the map","visible_text_on_image":"Central Lake","why_safe_to_show":"Major geographical feature used for relative spatial directions."},{"name":"North Gate","position":"Top centre","visible_text_on_image":"North Gate","why_safe_to_show":"Orientation point at the top of the map."},{"name":"The Old Bridge","position":"On the west path crossing a small stream","visible_text_on_image":"Old Bridge","why_safe_to_show":"Reference point for navigation on the west path."}],"visible_labels":[{"label":"A","position":"Just to the right of the Main Entrance","is_answer_label":false,"hidden_correct_place_or_part":"Staff Parking (former cafe)","visual_appearance":"neutral shape only","visual_neutrality_rule":"Do not reveal this answer or distractor through icons, objects, signs, products, tools, furniture, symbols, vehicles, or semantic visu