747	994	listening_tests	e5acc5d3-aa5a-4ca8-ae62-346b88e99653	{"id":"e5acc5d3-aa5a-4ca8-ae62-346b88e99653","title":"Greenfield Golf Course Facilities","slug":"greenfield-golf-course-facilities","description":"A map of Greenfield Golf Course showing the main entrance, clubhouse, car park, and six labelled locations across the course grounds.","accent":"British English","duration_seconds":null,"question_count":5,"is_free":true,"instruction_text":"Label the map below. Write the correct letter, A-F, next to Questions 1-5.","transcript":"Welcome to Greenfield Golf Course. I am going to describe a few of the key facilities around the course so you know exactly where to find everything before you head out.\\n\\nWhen you first arrive, the main entrance is at the bottom of the site. Just to the right of the entrance, on the east side, you will find the buggy hire point. This is the first building you pass as you come through the gate, so it is very easy to spot.\\n\\nAs you walk north along the main path, the building on your left, roughly halfway up, is our professional shop. This is where you can buy equipment, clothing, and accessories. It is worth noting that the storage building up near the clubhouse, also on the left, is not open to visitors.\\n\\nIf you continue along the main path and take the side path heading east near the centre of the course, you will reach the refreshment kiosk at the far end. It serves hot drinks and light snacks throughout the day.\\n\\nBack on the main path, just before you reach the side path turning, there is a practice area on the right. This is the putting green, where you can warm up before your round.\\n\\nFinally, if you need any medical assistance during your visit, the first aid point is on the right side of the map, in the lower section, south of the refreshment kiosk. Please do make a note of its location before you start.","prosody_script":null,"date_created":"2026-06-18T14:54:42.235Z","date_updated":"2026-06-18T14:54:42.235Z","status":"published","metadata":{"schema_version":"visual_labelling_listening_v1","topic":"Golf Course Map","speaker_role":"golf course staff member giving a welcome tour","image_generation_prompt":"Create a clean, flat-style outdoor golf course map in landscape orientation. The map has three fixed orientation landmarks with printed text: 'Main Entrance' at the bottom centre, 'Car Park' at the bottom left, and 'Clubhouse' at the top centre. A main path runs from the Main Entrance northward to the Clubhouse. A side path branches east from the main path near the centre of the map. Place six letter labels on the map as follows: label A is a neutral rectangular area at the bottom right near the Main Entrance on the east side; label B is a neutral rectangular area on the left side midway up the map beside the main path; label C is a neutral area in the centre of the map just east of the main path; label D is a neutral rectangular area at the top left near the Clubhouse; label E is a neutral area at the top right at the far end of the side path; label F is a neutral area on the right side in the lower section south of label E. All six labelled locations must appear as plain neutral blocks or shapes with no icons, no symbols, no signs, no furniture, no vehicles, no tools, no products, no pictograms, and no text other than their letter label. The map should include simple grass areas, light path lines, and gentle landscape shading. Do not add any visual clue that reveals the function or purpose of any labelled location.","difficulty_notes":{"word_count":239,"visible_label_count":6,"question_count":5,"distractor_label_count":1,"why_this_level":"B1: 239 words, 5 questions, 6 labels (A-F), 1 distractor label (D - storage building), one light distractor in transcript (storage building mentioned but marked as not open to visitors), multi-step directions used, phrases such as just to the right, roughly halfway up, at the far end, just before, south of.","distractors":["Label D (storage building near the clubhouse) is mentioned in the transcript as not open to visitors, making it a plausible distractor for the pro shop question."],"key_phrases":["just to the right of the entrance","roughly halfway up","take the side path heading east","at the far end","just before you reach the side path turning","south of the refreshment kiosk"],"visual_fairness_check":{"can_learners_guess_answers_from_image_alone":false,"anti_leak_checked":true,"notes":"All six labelled areas are visually neutral blocks. No icons, symbols, or objects are used. Fixed orientation landmarks (Main Entrance, Clubhouse, Car Park) do not reveal any answer. Learners must listen to identify all five answers."}}},"questions_public_json":{"groups":[{"id":"g1","type":"map_labelling","title":"Questions 1-5","instruction":"Label the map below. Write the correct letter, A-F, next to Questions 1-5.","question_range":{"from":1,"to":5},"media":{"image":{"type":"image","field":"image_file"},"audio":{"type":"audio","field":"audio_file"}},"options":{"type":"letters","values":["A","B","C","D","E","F"]},"questions":[{"id":"q1","number":1,"text":"Buggy Hire","input_type":"select","score":1},{"id":"q2","number":2,"text":"Pro Shop","input_type":"select","score":1},{"id":"q3","number":3,"text":"Refreshment Kiosk","input_type":"select","score":1},{"id":"q4","number":4,"text":"Putting Green","input_type":"select","score":1},{"id":"q5","number":5,"text":"First Aid Point","input_type":"select","score":1}]}]},"questions_answer_json":[{"id":"q1","correct_answer":"A","acceptable_answers":["A"],"score":1,"explanation":"The buggy hire point is on the east side, just to the right of the main entrance, which matches label A at the bottom right near the entrance.","transcript_evidence":"Just to the right of the entrance, on the east side, you will find the buggy hire point."},{"id":"q2","correct_answer":"B","acceptable_answers":["B"],"score":1,"explanation":"The pro shop is on the left side of the main path, roughly halfway up the course, which matches label B on the left side midway up the map.","transcript_evidence":"As you walk north along the main path, the building on your left, roughly halfway up, is our professional shop."},{"id":"q3","correct_answer":"E","acceptable_answers":["E"],"score":1,"explanation":"The refreshment kiosk is at the far end of the side path heading east from the centre of the course, which matches label E at the top right at the far end of the side path.","transcript_evidence":"If you continue along the main path and take the side path heading east near the centre of the course, you will reach the refreshment kiosk at the far end."},{"id":"q4","correct_answer":"C","acceptable_answers":["C"],"score":1,"explanation":"The putting green is on the right side of the main path just before the side path turning, which matches label C in the centre just east of the main path.","transcript_evidence":"Back on the main path, just before you reach the side path turning, there is a practice area on the right. This is the putting green."},{"id":"q5","correct_answer":"F","acceptable_answers":["F"],"score":1,"explanation":"The first aid point is on the right side, in the lower section, south of the refreshment kiosk, which matches label F on the right side lower area south of label E.","transcript_evidence":"The first aid point is on the right side of the map, in the lower section, south of the refreshment kiosk."}],"thumbnail":null,"map_image":null,"type":"map_labelling","topic":null,"tests_taken":"0","level":"B1","audio_file":[]}	{"status":"published"}	\N	\N
