 Aid Post is located in the bottom-right corner of the map, having swapped locations with the Volunteer Rest Zone, marked as label D.","transcript_evidence":"the first building you'll see in the bottom-right corner is the First Aid Post."},{"id":"q6","correct_answer":"E","acceptable_answers":["E"],"score":1,"explanation":"The Gourmet Dessert Stand is located about halfway up the eastern path, marked as label E.","transcript_evidence":"Moving further north along that eastern path, about halfway up, is the Gourmet Dessert Stand"},{"id":"q7","correct_answer":"F","acceptable_answers":["F"],"score":1,"explanation":"The Vegetarian Kitchen is located in the top-right corner of the map, next to the recycling area, marked as label F.","transcript_evidence":"Finally, if you keep going all the way to the top-right corner, next to the waste recycling area, you'll find the Vegetarian Kitchen"}],"thumbnail":null,"map_image":"66d4ddf8-a70e-4d56-ab92-aac6d696ff67","type":"map_labelling","topic":null,"tests_taken":"0","level":"C1","audio_file":[11]}	{"status":"published","map_image":"66d4ddf8-a70e-4d56-ab92-aac6d696ff67"}	\N	\N
