761	1014	directus_files	fa49bb7e-278f-48f4-8765-72fd0a638b11	{"folder":"4a56719f-2169-430c-b5fe-aa5162c9ccde","title":"Dairy Farm B2 20260918 180911 Map","filename_download":"dairy-farm_b2_20260918_180911_map.png","type":"image/png","storage":"local"}	{"folder":"4a56719f-2169-430c-b5fe-aa5162c9ccde","title":"Dairy Farm B2 20260918 180911 Map","filename_download":"dairy-farm_b2_20260918_180911_map.png","type":"image/png","storage":"local"}	\N	\N
762	1015	listening_tests	6fffbc7c-f487-48f4-b3e2-d6c6cacec035	{"id":"6fffbc7c-f487-48f4-b3e2-d6c6cacec035","title":"Meadowbrook Dairy Farm Tour","slug":"meadowbrook-dairy-farm-tour","description":"A map of a dairy farm with paths, buildings, and an entrance.","accent":"British English","duration_seconds":null,"question_count":6,"is_free":true,"instruction_text":"Label the map below. Write the correct letter, A-H, next to Questions 1-6.","transcript":"Welcome everyone to the Meadowbrook Dairy Farm. We are thrilled to have you here for our afternoon tour. Before we set off, please take a look at the maps I've just handed out so you can get your bearings. You'll see we are currently standing at the Main Entrance, which is at the bottom of your map.\\n\\nIf you look straight ahead from the entrance, along the main path on the left hand side, you'll see a large building. That is the Cheese Shop. We originally planned to put the farm museum there, but our cheese production expanded so much we needed the extra space for sales instead.\\n\\nContinuing up the main path, you'll notice it splits into two directions. If you follow the left branch, right at the very end of that path is the Milking Barn. We have a viewing gallery there where you can watch the afternoon milking session.\\n\\nNow, just opposite the Milking Barn, across the path on the right hand side, is a smaller structure. That's the Calf Shed. We've got several newborn calves in there at the moment, which are always very popular with our visitors.\\n\\nLet's go back to where the main path split. If you take the right branch this time, you'll soon reach a corner. Just beyond this corner, on the right hand side of the path, is our Farm Museum. It houses some fascinating historical farming equipment. You might also notice another building marked on the far right of the map, just before you reach the museum. That used to be the old tractor shed, but it's currently closed for renovations, so please don't try to go in there.\\n\\nMoving past the museum, the path continues towards the top right of the map. At the very end of this path is the Pasture Gate. We'll be heading there later to see the main herd grazing in the fields.\\n\\nFinally, if you're looking for somewhere to eat your lunch, we have a lovely Picnic Area. From the main entrance, if you look to your immediate right, there's a short side path leading to a circular space. That's the picnic area. It's a great spot to relax. I should also point out that the area immediately to the left of the entrance is just staff parking, so please keep clear of that section.\\n\\nAlright, if everyone is ready, let's begin our tour...","prosody_script":null,"date_created":"2026-06-18T14:54:52.590Z","date_updated":"2026-06-18T14:54:52.590Z","status":"published","metadata":{"schema_version":"visual_labelling_listening_v1","topic":"Dairy Farm","speaker_role":"Tour Guide","image_generation_prompt":"An outdoor map layout of a dairy farm. At the bottom center, there is a fixed text label 'Main Entrance'. A main path leads north from the entrance and splits into a left branch and a right branch. Provide visible letter labels A to H in the following neutral locations: Label A is a building shape along the left side of the main path. Label B is at the far end of the left branch. Label C is a building shape opposite Label B, on the right side of the left branch. Label D is a building shape past a corner on the right branch, located on the right side of the path. Label E is a shape on the far right of the map, positioned before reaching Label D. Label F is a shape at the very end of the right path towards the top right. Label G is a circular space down a short side path to the immediate right of the main entrance. Label H is a shape immediately to the left of the main entrance. All labeled locations must be visually neutral shapes (e.g., plain buildings or areas). Do not draw any icons, cows, cheese, tractors, picnic tables, cars, signs, or products that reveal the functions of the locations. The map should be clean and clear.","difficulty_notes":{"word_count":400,"visible_label_count":8,"question_count":6,"distractor_label_count":2,"why_this_level":"Includes multi-step directions, changed locations (museum to cheese shop), negations (closed for renovations), and natural distractors.","distractors":["farm museum originally planned for cheese shop location","old tractor shed","staff parking"],"key_phrases":["straight ahead","splits into two directions","opposite","just beyond this corner","far right","immediate right"],"visual_fairness_check":{"can_learners_guess_answers_from_image_alone":false,"anti_leak_checked":true,"notes":"All answer locations are described as neutral shapes in the prompt."}}},"questions_public_json":{"groups":[{"id":"g1","type":"map_labelling","title":"Questions 1-6","instruction":"Label the map below. Write the correct letter, A-H, next to Questions 1-6.","question_range":{"from":1,"to":6},"media":{"image":{"type":"image","field":"image_file"},"audio":{"type":"audio","field":"audio_file"}},"options":{"type":"letters","values":["A","B","C","D","E","F","G","H"]},"questions":[{"id":"q1","number":1,"text":"Cheese Shop","input_type":"select","score":1},{"id":"q2","number":2,"text":"Milking Barn","input_type":"select","score":1},{"id":"q3","number":3,"text":"Calf Shed","input_type":"select","score":1},{"id":"q4","number":4,"text":"Farm Museum","input_type":"select","score":1},{"id":"q5","number":5,"text":"Pasture Gate","input_type":"select","score":1},{"id":"q6","number":6,"text":"Picnic Area","input_type":"select","score":1}]}]},"questions_answer_json":[{"id":"q1","correct_answer":"A","acceptable_answers":["A"],"score":1,"explanation":"The Cheese Shop is the large building along the main path on the left hand side.","transcript_evidence":"along the main path on the left hand side, you'll see a large building. That is the Cheese Shop."},{"id":"q2","correct_answer":"B","acceptable_answers":["B"],"score":1,"explanation":"The Milking Barn is at the very end of the left branch of the main path.","transcript_evidence":"If you follow the left branch, right at the very end of that path is the Milking Barn."},{"id":"q3","correct_answer":"C","acceptable_answers":["C"],"score":1,"explanation":"The Calf Shed is opposite the Milking Barn, across the path on the right hand side.","transcript_evidence":"just opposite the Milking Barn, across the path on the right hand side, is a smaller structure. That's the Calf Shed."},{"id":"q4","correct_answer":"D","acceptable_answers":["D"],"score":1,"explanation":"The Farm Museum is just beyond the corner on the right branch, on the right hand side of the path.","transcript_evidence":"take the right branch... Just beyond this corner, on the right hand side of the path, is our Farm Museum."},{"id":"q5","correct_answer":"F","acceptable_answers":["F"],"score":1,"explanation":"The Pasture Gate is at the very end of the path that continues towards the top right of the map.","transcript_evidence":"the path continues towards the top right of the map. At the very end of this path is the Pasture Gate."},{"id":"q6","correct_answer":"G","acceptable_answers":["G"],"score":1,"explanation":"The Picnic Area is a circular space down a short side path to the immediate right of the main entrance.","transcript_evidence":"From the main entrance, if you look to your immediate right, there's a short side path leading to a circular space. That's the picnic area."}],"thumbnail":null,"map_image":"fa49bb7e-278f-48f4-8765-72fd0a638b11","type":"map_labelling","topic":null,"tests_taken":"0","level":"B2","audio_file":[12]}	{"map_image":"fa49bb7e-278f-48f4-8765-72fd0a638b11"}	\N	\N
