es typical of B2 such as 'far side of', 'just beyond', 'directly opposite', and 'before you reach'.","distractors":["The old cafe location near the entrance which is now staff parking.","The maintenance shed near the North Gate which could be mistaken for the cafe."],"key_phrases":["straight ahead","no longer open","instead","far side of","just beyond","directly opposite","before you reach","just past"],"visual_fairness_check":{"can_learners_guess_answers_from_image_alone":false,"anti_leak_checked":true,"notes":"Every letter label corresponds to an identical, completely featureless geometric shape. There are absolutely no signs, trees, tables, or icons depicting coffee cups, bicycles, or presents. The answers can only be determined by listening to the spatial directions in the talk."}},"audio_preparation":{"audio_engine":"ElevenLabs v3","needs_audio_script_conversion":true,"do_not_put_audio_tags_in_transcript":true,"transcript_style":"clean plain English"}}	{"groups":[{"id":"g1","type":"map_labelling","title":"Questions 1-6","instruction":"Label the map below. Write the correct letter, A-H, next to Questions 1-6.","question_range":{"from":1,"to":6},"media":{"image":{"type":"image","field":"image_file"},"audio":{"type":"audio","field":"audio_file"}},"options":{"type":"letters","values":["A","B","C","D","E","F","G","H"]},"questions":[{"id":"q1","number":1,"text":"Visitor Centre","input_type":"select","score":1},{"id":"q2","number":2,"text":"Cafe","input_type":"select","score":1},{"id":"q3","number":3,"text":"Boat Hire","input_type":"select","score":1},{"id":"q4","number":4,"text":"Rose Garden","input_type":"select","score":1},{"id":"q5","number":5,"text":"Children's Playground","input_type":"select","score":1},{"id":"q6","number":6,"text":"Picnic Area","input_type":"select","score":1}]}]}	[{"id":"q1","correct_answer":"B","acceptable_answers":["B"],"score":1,"explanation":"The Visitor Centre is the large building straight ahead from the Main Entrance, just before you r